### **4. Replace Email**
- Find `[YOUR EMAIL HERE]` in the code
- Replace it with your actual email address

### **5. Commit the File**
- Scroll down
- Click "Commit new file"

### **6. Enable GitHub Pages**
- Go to repository "Settings" (top menu)
- Scroll down to "Pages" section (left sidebar)
- Under "Source", select "Deploy from a branch"
- Choose "main" branch
- Click "Save"

### **7. Get Your URL**
- Wait 1-2 minutes
- Your privacy policy will be live at:
```
  https://[YOUR-GITHUB-USERNAME].github.io/beyondfit-privacy/
